reviewText: Watching Jerry is not as fun as listening to him.  I didn't find this to be the best of his works by far, though perhaps still a good purchase if you're a die-hard Clower fan.
Title: Jerry Clower: Classic Clower Power

reviewText: This guy is still humorous and clean and may not be everyone's cup of tea but I bet you can find a laugh or two even if you feel you are too sophisticated for Jerry. I really enjoyed the older versions of his humor more though.
Title: Jerry Clower: Classic Clower Power

reviewText: I only llistened to this once & enjoyed it.  It was a birthday gift for my son-in-law & he LOVED it!!!  Therefore I am very happy with this product!
Title: Jerry Clower: Classic Clower Power

reviewText: Jerry Clower was one of the great humorists of the 20th century. Someone once said that a comedian told funny stories, but a humoristtold stories funny. Jerry Clower was one of the best. He could make striking a match funny. Think of him as a country version ofBill Cosby.This collection includes two of Clowers live appearances. He`ll have you rolling on the floor with his tales and stories. You willnot be disappointed.
summary: One of the great humorists of the 20th century
Title: Jerry Clower: Classic Clower Power

reviewText: Jerry Clower is a very funny story teller. Nothing dirty,or degrading. He is just an old country boy telling about what goes on around him. He is great.
summary: Very funny man. I listened to him as a kid. Loved him then as now.
Title: Jerry Clower: Classic Clower Power

reviewText: This was just what I wanted and anticipated. A high quality dvd that is well put together and plays perfectly.
Title: Jerry Clower: Classic Clower Power
